Furthermore, the paper proposes a new architecture for NMT, which involves the use of multiple context vectors, which is a common topic in the cs.LG (Learning) sub-category. 

The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which makes it likely to belong to the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
